2017-12-10  Nicolas Léveillé  <nicolas@uucidl.com>
    * release: 1.0.1, 1.0.0
    * passing None to package_name still results
      in valid xml (using Use xml.etree.ElementTree, thanks to
      Diez Roggish <dir@ableton.com>)
    * XML is generated as UTF-8

